dc_description_s: This dataset contains the existing Hennepin County on-and off-street bikeway system as defined by the 2040 Bicycle Transportation Plan. The current Hennepin County and Three Rivers Park District bikeway system includes 651 miles of on- and off-street bikeways, 140 miles of which are regional trails operated by the park district. This dataset represents the existing Hennepin County bikeway system, which includes regional, municipal, state and county on-street and off-street bikeways. This dataset does not represent all on- and off-street bikeways in Hennepin County.
